## Bot Commands Reference

### Invitation & Vetting
- `/invite @username [context]` - Invite someone (counts as first vouch)
- `/vouch @username` - Vouch for invitee or existing member

### Trust Management
- `/flag @username [reason]` - Flag member (required reason)

### Status Queries
- `/status` - Your trust standing
- `/mesh` - Network overview (trust + replication health)
- `/mesh strength` - DVR and vouch distribution
- `/mesh replication` - Replication health status
- `/mesh config` - Group configuration

### Configuration
- `/propose config <setting> <value>` - Signal group settings
- `/propose stroma <setting> <value>` - Stroma configuration
- `/propose federate <group-id>` - Federation proposal

### Audit
- `/audit operator` - Operator action history

