## State Transitions

### Invitee ‚Üí Bridge ‚Üí Validator
- Invitee (1 vouch, outside group)
- Bridge (2 vouches, in group)
- Validator (3+ vouches, in group)

### Member ‚Üí Ejected ‚Üí Re-Entry
- Ejection: Standing < 0 OR Effective_Vouches < 2
- Re-entry: Secure 2 new vouches via /invite
- No cooldown period
